| **Groq**              | `GROQ_API_KEY`         | `groq/model-name`                |
| **Helicone**          | `HELICONE_API_KEY`     | `helicone/model-name`            |
| **Hugging Face**      | `HF_TOKEN`             | `huggingface/model-name`         |
| **Hyperbolic**        | `HYPERBOLIC_API_KEY`   | `hyperbolic/model-name`          |
